    "description": "FitOn Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Visual Merchandiser at our Bhubaneswar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout FitOn Holdings Services:\nFitOn Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FitOn Holdings Services!",
